  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA56">
<l>niṟamveḷitu ceytu pacitu kariteṉ</l>
<l>ṟiṟaiyuruvam yāmaṟiyō meṇṇi – ṉiṟaivuṭaiya</l>
<l>nāmaṅkai tāṉu nalampukaḻa vallaḷē</l>
<l>pūmaṅkai kēḷvaṉ polivu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>‘[His] colours are white, red, green, black’:</l>
<l>if we count thus we won’t know the form of the lord. In [her] profusion</l>
<l>the Lady of the tongue  alone is capable of praising the goodness,</l>
<l>the splendour of the husband of the Lady from the flower.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
